727431f-a.title: Queens: Metropolitan Avenue - 78th Street
727431f-a.text:
Metropoiitan Avenue, north side, west of 78th Street, showing in three views in order from fore to hackground the Abraham Folk blaclsmith shop and house, a doubie two story structure, J. Schneider's
Middle Village Hoteu, and the M.E. Church of Newtown.
October 1923
View 2:1922
View 3:Fehruary 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
